Firestrike slowed, the finally came to a stop.  "Well. " the rhino 
said, as it transformed into the 16 foot robot mode.  "Nice to see 
you wield a worth weapon.  Hah" he laughed as he slowy withdrew 
his 7 foot long, thee foot wide sword.  With no button the sword 
ignited in a a blazing red flame.  "I am also glad i get to use my 
weapon of choice."  he slowly began walking at Icedemon.  He was 
going to let him make the first move.
